    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, this car is ready for its next adventure! It\u2019s clean, runs great, and I\u2019ve taken really good care of it. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love it!",
      "price": 34500.0,
