    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS for exceptional throttle response. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a 3.62 limited-slip differential. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced with plates to ensure structural integrity under lateral load. The suspension retains its precision through Bilstein dampers and refreshed bushings, while the braking system utilizes cross-drilled rotors for effective heat dissipation. Documented valve clearances and a recent rod bearing service make this a mechanically robust example of BMW's M-division engineering.",
